Package Custom_CollectionsED.nodes

Class DoubleNode<T>

java.lang.Object
Custom_CollectionsED.nodes.DoubleNode<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The data type to be stored in the nodes.
public class DoubleNode<T> extends Object
This classes serves as a representation of a double node, to be used when handling doubly linked lists. Each node contains references to the preceding, and succeeding nodes.
